Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.11,0:00:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.71,0:00:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.86,0:00:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗噗噗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.86,0:00:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨~大家好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.63,0:00:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.92,0:00:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是DJ潘恩AND蒂德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.11,0:00:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.50,0:00:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何，什麼，為什麼\N有問必答單元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.87,0:00:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.07,0:00:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何卡修王會打贏阿修拉姆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.27,0:00:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上的問題，我們就請記者\N西莉絲小姐為我們做個專訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.88,0:00:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來西莉絲西莉絲，麻煩妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.25,0:00:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是拱門之路前的西莉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.48,0:00:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃，卡修王為何能打贏那\N嚴謹的阿修拉姆呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.20,0:00:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這謎底大家都很想知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.73,0:01:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪門子的問題啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.53,0:01:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.20,0:01:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這身為佛雷姆的傭兵王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.34,0:01:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會輸給那\N初出茅廬的小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.27,0:01:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是據聞阿修拉姆手上有\N魔劍碎魂這把強力的劍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.67,0:01:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這點?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.43,0:01:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼，魔劍碎魂?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.22,0:01:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔，又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.18,0:01:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡修王，您那詭異的笑容\N難. 不. 成…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.42,0:01:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎魂又算得了什麼!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.72,0:01:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不輸給魔劍\N(魔劍音同"不輸")
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.73,0:01:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.86,0:01:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄戰爭是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.77,0:01:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是個好問題呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.27,0:01:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓我們就來"探觸"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.87,0:01:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前貝魯德皇帝\N所引起的英雄戰爭吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.25,0:01:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探"觸"到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.61,0:01:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，今天的節目就到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.78,0:01:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見!再見!再見!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.36,0:01:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.09,0:01:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看喔
